column1: # CardDemo Daily Transaction Test Data - CSV Format
# Comprehensive test fixture supporting Spring Batch FlatFileItemReader transaction processing
# Migrated from COBOL fixed-width format (app/data/ASCII/dailytran.txt) to CSV structure
# - account_id: 11-digit account number for account linking
# - description: Transaction description for audit trail
# - merchant_zip: Merchant ZIP code (up to 10 characters)
# - transaction_timestamp: ISO 8601 timestamp for PostgreSQL partitioning
# - Various merchant locations and ZIP codes
# - Different card numbers for cross-reference testing
# - Timestamp distribution across multiple months for partitioning validation
# - Exact decimal representation without floating-point errors
# - Negative amounts for returns/refunds properly handled
# Created: Daily transaction CSV fixture for comprehensive Spring Batch testing
